    score: '2.00',
    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '20',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      "A Conflict of Interest policy is essential for NFPs in order to:\n \n - protect the organisation's assets and reputation,\n - enhance transparency and accountability, and\n - meet compliance requirements.\n\nThe Board should establish definitively whether it has a valid Conflict of Interest policy.  Any existing document should be cross-referenced against a suitable template such as that provided by the ACNC https:\/\/www.acnc.gov.au\/tools\/templates\/conflict-interest-policy (c) Commonwealth of Australia 2018.\n\nThe Board should also ensure it has established a conflict of interest register.  Again, a helpful template is provided by the ACNC https:\/\/www.acnc.gov.au\/tools\/templates\/register-interests (c) Commonwealth of Australia 2018.",
    created_at: '2024-09-10 21:49:50',
    updated_at: '2025-01-29 06:06:49',
