    detailed: null,
    score: '2.00',
    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '20',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Every NFP of any organisation structure type must have an appropriate Privacy Policy documented.  Such a document is crucial for protecting stakeholder information, compliance with Privacy regulations, building stakeholder trust and credibility, enhancing transparency and mitigating data risks.\n\nIf you are unsure how well your current Privacy Policy covers the requirements of your organisation, the Board should commission a task to review the existing documentation against a decent external template in the public domain such as that provided by the Business Victoria (Victorian Government) https:\/\/business.vic.gov.au\/tools-and-templates\/privacy-policy-template.',
    created_at: '2024-09-10 21:49:50',
    updated_at: '2025-01-29 06:24:50',
