    action_text:
      'Please read the following definition of governance:\n\nThe term "governance" is often associated with the process of steering, guiding, and leading an organisation. It encompasses the mechanisms, processes, and relations by which an organisation is controlled and directed. Effective governance involves making decisions, setting priorities, and ensuring that the organisation\'s objectives are met while taking into account the interests of various stakeholders. In essence, governance is about providing direction, oversight, and leadership to achieve the goals of an organisation.',
