      'Please read the following regarding NFP membership:\n\nA Constitution comprises a number of sections, one of which is Membership.  Details regarding membership eligibility, rights, responsibilities, and the process for becoming a member are outlined in this section. It may also cover issues related to membership fees, voting rights, and termination of membership.\n\nSimilarly, Model Rules also define eligibility for Membership, including who is eligible to become a member of the organisation. This may include individuals, organisations, or specific categories of stakeholders.',
