    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '20',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      "While the Board is responsible for Financial policies, they are also responsible for policies that relate to strategic direction, overseeing governance, and ensuring the organisation's effectiveness.  Critical policies that the Board must oversee include:\n\n - Code of Ethics and Conduct\n - Conflict of Interest Policy\n - Whistleblower Protection Policy\n - Financial Policies\n - Fundraising Policy\n - Risk Management Policy\n - Strategic Plan\n - Succession Planning Policy\n - Board Governance Policies\n - Data Privacy and Protection Policy",
    created_at: '2024-09-10 21:49:50',
    updated_at: '2025-03-05 04:02:44',
