      "It is good practice for key documents to be readily (preferably electronically) available to Board members whenever they need it.  The Board should ensure that the organisation's Diversity and Inclusion Policy is stored appropriately and that Board members know how to access it at any time.",
    created_at: '2024-09-10 21:49:50',
