    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '30',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      "A delegations instrument clearly outlines the authority, responsibilities, and decision-making powers delegated by the board to specific individuals, committees, or staff members within the organisation.   \n\nThe Board should confirm whether or not it has a current delegations instrument in play.  If not, it should move to implement such an instrument with urgency; consider GovernApp's Template: Organisational Delegations as a starting point.",
    created_at: '2024-09-10 21:49:50',
    updated_at: '2024-10-16 06:38:19',
