    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '10',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'The Board should commit to regular - ideally annual - CEO performance reviews.  The frequency of the review process should be defined as part of the review process itself.  It is helpful to diarise the process well in advance of the due date; to ensure continuity, the date can be pencilled in as the previous review is closed out.\n',
