    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Standard 2.3 requires that "members of the organisation’s governing body must meet the ACNC’s suitability requirements".  To that end, you must ensure that current Board members should be checked against the ASIC Disqualified Persons Register to ensure that no Board members have been disqualified from Board roles by ASIC.  \n\nYour organisation should implement a process to ensure that all current Board members are checked against the ASIC Disqualified Persons Register every year.',
