    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'A comprehensive Conflict of Interest policy should address how to disclose or manage conflicts of interest.\n \nThe Board should review and update its Conflict of Interest policy using a suitable template such as that provided by the ACNC https:\/\/www.acnc.gov.au\/tools\/templates\/conflict-interest-policy (c) Commonwealth of Australia 2018.\n\nThe CMASC has also published a basic Policy for Excellence in Handling Conflicts of Interest, available at https:\/\/www.cmasc.net.au\/principles-standards\/supporting-policies.\n\nThe Board should also establish a conflict of interest register.  Again, a helpful template is provided by the ACNC https:\/\/www.acnc.gov.au\/tools\/templates\/register-interests (c) Commonwealth of Australia 2018.',
