    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Standard 6.2 requires that "the governing body must ensure that the reports provided to it contain sufficient detail, in appropriate formats, to allow it to determine the financial health and performance of the organisation".  \n\nIf Board is finding that it often needs additional data to fully understand the organisation\'s financial position, recommended remedial actions to undertake are:\n\n - Incorporate additional data (e.g., budget vs. actuals, financial ratios, fundraising outcomes) into the standard reporting package.\n - Survey Board members to identify recurring data requests and adjust reports to include these elements proactively.\n - Use software to create a visual dashboard that provides an at-a-glance overview of key metrics.\n - Establish a process for ongoing dialogue between the Board and finance team to anticipate information needs.',
