      'Standard 6.5 requires that "each year the governing body must review... any audit report and \/ or management letter provided by the auditor".\n\nThe Board should ensure that it reviews any audit report and \/ or management letter provided by the auditor every year.  This can be completed in association with the review of the financial reports.\n\nThis review should be recorded in meeting minutes.',
