    action_text:
      'Standard 6.5 requires that "each year the governing body must review... any audit report and \/ or management letter provided by the auditor".\n\nThe Board should ensure that it schedules and conducts a review of any audit report and \/ or management letter provided by the auditor as they become available each year.  This can be completed in association with the review of the financial reports.\n\nThis review should be recorded in meeting minutes.',
