    action_text:
      'Standard 6.5 requires that "each year the governing body must review... any audit report and \/ or management letter provided by the auditor".\n\nThe Board should ensure that its reviews of audit report and \/ or management letters provided by the auditor is formally documented and that the review is recorded in meeting minutes.',
