    action_text:
      'Standard 8.2 requires that "the organisation must produce an annual report which is available to members, donors, staff, volunteers and members of the public".\n\nThe Board should ensure that an Annual Report is generated consistently every year.  It is recommended that this occurs at a set time period after the end of your financial year; this helps members, Board members and staff with expectations about timing and the timelines by which key artefacts (financials, impact reports, program reports etc) need to be ready.',
