    score: '4.00',
    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '10',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Standard 8.7 requires that "the organisation must maintain and publicise a mechanism for members, donors, staff, volunteers and other interested parties to submit feedback or register a complaint with the organisation...".\n\nPhysical suggestion boxes alone are not ideal as they require  person to be in attendance to provide feedback.  Consider the additional options of:\n\n - online feedback and complaints forms on your website;\n - a designated feedback \/ complaints email address.\n - a phone number where stakeholders can speak to a representative or leave a voicemail;\n - Social Media (follower comments); and\n - a mailing address for written feedback \/ complaints to be mailed to.',
    created_at: '2025-01-14 08:34:50',
