    action_text:
      'Standard 9.3 requires that "the organisation supply appropriate data on its receipts to donors for tax deductible gifts".  \n\nThe Board should ensure that the organisation includes all of the following data on its tax deductible receipts:\n\n - the name of the donor (can be an organisation name);\n - your organisation’s name;\n - your organisation ABN\n - the amount donated\n - date(s) of the donations, and;\n - a statement that the donation is tax-deductible.',
