      'While the legal requirements of Board composition change across states (for Incorporated Associations), NFP Boards should comprise of a Chair (or President), Vice-Chair; Secretary, and a Treasurer. Ordinary Board members with either a specific or without a specific portfolio may be elected as well.  In NSW, Incorporated Associations must also elect 3 general Board members in addition to these core roles.',
