    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'The Board should commit to ensuring a transparent, merit based recruitment process for all Board positions if it indeed has the capacity to do so.  \n\nThere are legitimate circumstances where a Board member is brought in on factors other than particular skills, such as extensive networks, historical financial support, or prior senior service to the organisation.  In all circumstances, the way in which a new Board member is engaged should always be transparent and subject to broader Board scrutiny.',
