    action_text:
      'A governance policy is a foundational framework that supports the effective and responsible management of a nonprofit organisation, ensuring alignment with its mission, compliance with legal requirements, and accountability to stakeholders.  While a governance policy covers much of the same ground as a Constitution \/ Model Rules, it is a useful summary and guide for ready access and public consumption.\n\nIt is recommended that all organisations have a Governance Policy.\n\nIf the Board is unsure about the status of its Governance Policy, it should move to confirm such a policy exists and make it accessible, or move to adopt a new Policy. \n\nSee our Template: Governance Policy for a helpful starting point.',
