    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Board succession planning will ensure continuity, leadership development, and the ability to adapt to changing circumstances for an NFP Board.  While discussions around the subject are helpful, to maximise transparency and preparedness, and to minimise the opportunity for misunderstanding, it is helpful to formally document your succession policy, associated procedure and the candidates you have identified and are cultivating for future Board roles.\n\nThe Board should develop a Board succession policy and appoint a Board member or a Committee to oversee the process.  Consider using our Template: Board Succession Policy and Procedure.',
