    risk_id: '10',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Working with Children checks are mandatory for all NFPs in some jurisdictions, and are mandatory in circumstances where organisations serve children, work in education or in health.  Your Childsafe Policy should have determined whether you require Working with Children checks in your jurisdiction and for the services you provide.  \n\nBoards should confirm that Working with Children checks are not required for their organisation and that this status is confirmed and documented in their Childsafe Policy.',
