    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'It is a requirement of almost all NFP jurisdictions that Board meeting minutes be published.  It is sound governance practice irrespective of the compliance driver.\n\nIt is extremely helpful for board minutes to accurately reflect how decisions were arrived at and the reasoning behind those decisions; doing so increases transparency and accountability. \n\nThe Board must start the process of taking minutes in Board meetings.  A helpful guide to minute  taking is provided in our Model Practice: Taking Effective Board Minutes.',
