    order: '2',
    text: 'We have a documented process internal to the organisation (not publicly available).',
    detailed: null,
    score: '8.00',
    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '10',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Transparency in NFP operations reinforces trust and stakeholder engagement.  The Board should publish the process by which eligible stakeholder can request access to documents that are not generally publicly available.\n\nThe process should ideally be published via the organisation website.',
    created_at: '2025-02-20 04:47:57',
