    risk_id: '10',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      "The Board should ensure that a consideration of solvency is part of their review of the organisation's financial status at every Board meeting, and that the minutes of Board meetings - or the AGM at the very least - also include a declaration of solvency.",
