    detailed: null,
    score: '4.00',
    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '20',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Intentional culture is a lever for for organisation to help achieve its core enduring purpose.  A lack of intentional culture risks bringing forward forces that mitigate against the core purpose.\n\nThe Board should consider thinking through, documenting and implementing an intentional culture that can increase alignment to purpose and strategy, and provide a platform to attract aligned people to the workforce.  Our Model Practice: Defining Intentional Culture will assist in the process.',
