    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      "The Board should review whether the organisation's charitable purpose is readily available to the public on the ACNC register and\/or on your organisation's website.  \n\nIf you have not already done so, or if you have not done so since it was most recently changed, you should upload your charity's governing document (your constitution, rules or trust deed) to the ACNC Charity Portal.  The ACNC will publish this information on its public ACNC Charity Register, which satisfies the definition of making your charity's purposes publicly available.\n\nPublishing your organisation's charitable purpose on your website is also recommended for maximum transparency.",
