    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Your assessment results suggest that the Board is unsure if the organisation is clear on how it deals with complaints from members.\n\nThe Board should review existing policies and procedures to ensure that:\n\n - There is a comprehensive process in place for receiving, assessing and responding to member complaints; \n - The process states the requirement to maintain records of complaints\n - The scope of the complaints process explicitly includes member complaints; and\n - The charity actually keeps records of members’ complaints and any associated resolutions.\n\nIf your organisation lacks one, the ACNC provides a template policy and procedure for complaints; see the link provided in your Action Plan.',
