    is_triggering_action: '1',
    risk_id: '20',
    is_na: '0',
    action_text:
      'Your Charity should have a defined process for the selection and appointment of Responsible Persons, and ensure that is is rigorously applied for all Responsible Persons prior to their appointment to your Board or other position. \n\nYou should ensure that the process includes:\n - A check of the ASIC Banned and Disqualified Register before a Responsible Person is appointed - see https:\/\/connectonline.asic.gov.au\/RegistrySearch\/faces\/landing\/SearchRegisters.jspx\n - A regular (eg. annual) search of the ASIC Banned and Disqualified Register for current Responsible People.\n - Retention of the search results records.\n\nYour Charity must not appoint a Responsible Person who has been disqualified from managing a corporation under the Corporations Act 2001 (Cth), or from being a Responsible Person by the ACNC Commissioner within the previous 12 months.',
    created_at: '2025-03-13 06:54:46',
